@Gateway = http://localhost:5047
@CorrelationId = tenant-http-001
@PlatformAdminToken = replace-with-platform-admin-jwt
@TenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create tenant (public onboarding, rate limited)
POST {{Gateway}}/tenants
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}

{
  "name": "Empresa Demo",
  "subdomain": "empresa-demo",
  "adminEmail": "admin@empresa-demo.com",
  "defaultTimeZoneId": "America/Santo_Domingo"
}

### List tenants (requires PlatformAdmin)
GET {{Gateway}}/tenants?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{PlatformAdminToken}}
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}

### Suspend tenant (requires PlatformAdmin)
PATCH {{Gateway}}/tenants/{{TenantId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{PlatformAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}

{
  "status": "Suspended"
}

### Gateway liveness
GET {{Gateway}}/health/live
